name: Emma Roberts
description:
Emma Roberts is an actress. She's been in a bunch of different tv shows and movies. I know her from American Horror Story.

About 37 reference photos were used here. Might have used a bit more but I think this works well enough to get some good photos generated with her likeness.

Let me know what you think and any suggestions on who to see next.

‌

If you like my work and wanna show me buy me a coffee
